30:["$","h3",null,{"children":"The Compound Effect"}]
31:["$","p",null,{"children":"The financial impact compounds over time in ways many business owners do not account for. A missed call today represents: the immediate job value (£250-£450), repeat business (2-3 additional jobs over 5 years), referral value (1-2 new customers), and review value (completed jobs generate Google reviews driving future enquiries)."}]
32:["$","p",null,{"children":"When combined, a single missed call can represent £1,500-£3,000 in total lifetime revenue loss. For a sole trader missing 20 calls per week, the annual compound loss can exceed £100,000."}]
